cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.MM, cs.AI, cs.IR 

The paper deals with video analysis and classification using convolutional neural networks, which is a common topic in computer vision (cs.CV). The proposed method also involves designing a lightweight neural network (cs.LG) and handling pairwise frame distances (cs.MM). The paper also involves classification tasks (cs.AI) and information retrieval (cs.IR) in terms of identifying repetitive activities in a video.
